06:00.908 --> 06:02.173
[ grunting ]

06:02.239 --> 06:03.372
Make attempt
to seize weapon,

06:03.439 --> 06:05.602
and I'll have your
fucking life.

06:05.670 --> 06:06.966
We move
for the ridge.

06:07.034 --> 06:08.396
Go!

06:08.464 --> 06:10.292
[ smashing ]

06:10.360 --> 06:11.890
Not much of a plan,
is it?

06:11.958 --> 06:14.121
