06:40.979 --> 06:42.541
[ yelling ]

06:42.609 --> 06:44.076
[ grunting ]
[ clanging ]

06:52.669 --> 07:00.827
[ yelling ]

07:00.895 --> 07:02.824
[ crackling ]

07:02.892 --> 07:05.423
They abandon hope
and burn the city.

07:05.490 --> 07:07.422
The rebels have
set torch to horreum.

07:07.490 --> 07:08.988
Three centuries have
been dispatched to quell --

07:09.055 --> 07:12.288
Recall them and move
towards commanded path.

07:12.356 --> 07:13.489
Imperator.

07:15.091 --> 07:18.154
Spartacus attempts
to turn victory into ash

07:18.218 --> 07:19.485
and you recall
your men?

07:19.552 --> 07:21.383
I have set plan
to motion,

07:21.451 --> 07:23.815
and will not fall
to distraction.

07:23.883 --> 07:25.745
We advance
on northern gate!

07:26.745 --> 07:27.677
Form up!

07:27.745 --> 07:31.013
[ grunting ]

07:31.081 --> 07:36.375
[ yelling ]

07:36.443 --> 07:38.005
Keep pace
and do not pause!

07:38.073 --> 07:39.598
Quickly!
Hurry!

07:39.666 --> 07:43.223
Move!

