09:03.989 --> 09:05.188
Bind his hands
and see him through the gate

09:05.256 --> 09:06.555
<i>with the others.</i>

09:06.623 --> 09:08.189
<i>Those who can fight</i>
<i>take rear position</i>

09:08.257 --> 09:09.217
