to the ridge!

09:09.257 --> 09:10.223
Take him!

09:10.291 --> 09:12.658
Move quickly,
and do not turn back!

09:12.725 --> 09:14.491
[ yelling, screaming ]

09:16.359 --> 09:21.295
[ CRACKLING ]

09:21.362 --> 09:23.063
Fall back!

09:23.131 --> 09:24.465
See all through
the gate!

09:26.300 --> 09:27.766
<i>Hold!</i>

09:31.802 --> 09:32.802
<i>Attack!</i>

09:32.869 --> 09:34.271
[ yelling ]

09:34.339 --> 09:36.205
[ yelling ]

09:36.273 --> 09:43.878
[ grunting ]
[ clanging ]

09:43.946 --> 09:45.478
<i>We must seal gate</i>
<i>behind us!</i>

09:51.850 --> 10:03.966
[ smashing ]

10:04.034 --> 10:10.154
[ crackling ]

10:10.222 --> 10:12.758
Oh, Crixus!

10:12.826 --> 10:14.462
Go!

10:21.878 --> 10:23.115
The man you seek.

10:23.182 --> 10:25.182
Spartacus!

10:25.250 --> 10:27.383
♪

10:32.761 --> 10:33.697
Seize him!

10:33.764 --> 10:41.044
[ yelling ]

10:41.112 --> 10:42.245
[ snapping ]

10:42.312 --> 10:43.411
<i>[ rumbling ]</i>

10:45.514 --> 10:48.149
[ yelling ]

10:48.217 --> 10:50.652
Even the gods grant
aid to the fucking man.

10:50.719 --> 10:53.357
They but delay
inevitable fall.

10:53.425 --> 10:54.425
Bring ram to bear.

10:54.493 --> 10:57.563
Sentries to guard
sundered gateway.

10:57.631 --> 10:58.833
We do not follow?

10:58.901 --> 11:00.237
In time.

11:00.305 --> 11:02.074
